Topic: 
    Database application to display data using data grid

Aim 

   To display a c# .net application using data grid view to display records


Procedure 
        
       * Open the c# .net window application project.
       * open toolbox , click the datagrid view tool and place it on the form by dragging the mouse .
       * Add a data source for the project and choose the database type a database 
       * Select the data connections and database object as the table 
       * Run The Application.

No coding only use tool box steps 
        

   
